        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-52" value="&quot;you&quot;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;textDirection=vertical-lr;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="890" y="630" width="30" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-53" value="&quot;zoo&quot;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;textDirection=vertical-lr;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="933" y="630" width="30" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-54" value="Input:" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="480" y="380" width="80" height="41" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-55" value="Targets:" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1050" y="380" width="110" height="41" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-56" value="1）该模型接收三个输入词元，并生成三个向量。" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fontColor=#000000;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#FFF9B2;strokeColor=none;fillStyle=solid;direction=west;gradientDirection=north;gradientColor=#FFF2A1;shadow=1;size=20;pointerEvents=1;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="380" y="565" width="210" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-57" value="2）模型生成的张量中的每个向量索引位置都对应于词汇表中的一个词。" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fontColor=#000000;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#FFF9B2;strokeColor=none;fillStyle=solid;direction=west;gradientDirection=north;gradientColor=#FFF2A1;shadow=1;size=20;pointerEvents=1;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="580" y="710" width="480" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-58" value="3) 未经训练的模型会为每个词元生成随机向量。" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fontColor=#000000;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#FFF9B2;strokeColor=none;fillStyle=solid;direction=west;gradientDirection=north;gradientColor=#FFF2A1;shadow=1;size=20;pointerEvents=1;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="640" y="350" width="340" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7E7r4uFxRQexS1e8NnOg-59" value="4) 在模型训练中，目标是最大化与目标向量中标记索引对应的值。" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fontColor=#000000;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#FFF9B2;strokeColor=none;fillStyle=solid;direction=west;gradientDirection=north;gradientColor=#FFF2A1;shadow=1;size=20;pointerEvents=1;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1030" y="580" width="230" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
