        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="4hMmltaJ_XPGaXl18vON-1" value="&lt;div&gt;In the realm of visual compositions,where content reigns&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;supreme, there exists a tranquil harbor known as&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Placeholder Bay.Here,amidst the gentle sway of design&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;elements,words meander without true purpose,yet with a&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;semblance of meaning. This text, neither too captivating nor&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;toobland,serves as a beacon foreyes that scan,seeking&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;the eventual substance that will fill the void. As the sun casts&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;fontSize=11;fontColor=default;labelBackgroundColor=default;spacing=8;align=left;arcSize=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="120" y="200" width="380" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="4hMmltaJ_XPGaXl18vON-2" value="&lt;div&gt;itsgoldenhues overPlaceholder Bay,sentences flowlike a&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;gentle river, words ripple like waves against the shore.&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Maple Mono NF CN;fontSize=11;fontColor=default;labelBackgroundColor=default;spacing=8;align=left;arcSize=15;" vertex="1" parent="1">
